Package: courtvisionr
Title: Cleans and Analyzes ATP/WTA Tennis Data
Version: 0.0.0.9000
Authors@R: 
    person("Brody", "Pinto", , "bjpint21@stlawu.edu", role = c("aut", "cre"),
           comment = c(ORCID = "YOUR-ORCID-ID"))
Description: This package includes functions to clean tennis data (to point-level and shot-level data) from the French Open major tournament (also called Roland Garros). The data includes ATP and WTA matches from 2019-2023. 
